Module vpm.gui_prototype
Package vpm.gui_prototype.models.FoodStuff

Class Food

java.lang.Object
vpm.gui_prototype.models.FoodStuff.Food
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFood
Direct Known Subclasses:
Bone, Milk, Pate, Pellets, Seed
public abstract class Food extends Object implements IFood
Abstract class representing food items for pets. This class implements the IFood interface and contains common properties and methods for various types of food.
